{"tid":2154173,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共產黨：定性香港作詞人林夕思想與中國主流民意相反 向香港民族文壇宣戰","createTime":"2020-08-13T03:40:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T04:13:25.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"455b83b86e4ef5cd15cfac5da92fc927ba0a75b7","tid":2154173,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T03:40:11.000Z","msg":"央視點名批評作詞人林夕為羅冠聰修改歌詞<br />\n<br />\n央視點名批評作詞人林夕跟「港獨」搞到一起，提到他早前為正身處外地的前香港眾志主席羅冠聰修改歌曲《約定》的歌詞，形容為林夕與「亂港分子」頭目的「約定」，反問林夕是否想誤導年輕人犧牲自己的青春年華，去當「政治燃料」。<br />\n<br />\n央視批評，林夕多年來一直參與政治運動，並從香港移居到台灣，曾填寫支持「佔中」的歌曲，在《蘋果日報》專欄撰寫批評、嘲諷內地的文章，受到「港獨」的追捧。評論認為，林夕的所作所為，與中華民族利益相背，與中國主流民意相反。文章又提到，林夕把為北京奧運寫歌詞一事說成「污點」，是顛倒黑白的解讀。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2352104\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2352104&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzo%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=bb774f3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2352104</a>"},{"pid":"7e50077e6e79cd7f709e4731d7528bcb5c0b664f","tid":2154173,"uid":55502,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T03:42:15.000Z","msg":"央視無一個文妓有資格批評林夕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36026b9c5a87fe4b5b579f27e8d3601a1562f41c","tid":2154173,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T04:07:01.000Z","msg":"我愛林直"},{"pid":"c5ac6a72ae1209dafca6f5b47f6826c746415c02","tid":2154173,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T04:13:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}